00:02:09.409 --> 00:02:10.409
That's amazing.

00:02:10.409 --> 00:02:12.969
So that's 40 years under ban.

00:02:12.969 --> 00:02:17.090
But now as I understand it, that's when both your families got the truth.

00:02:17.090 --> 00:02:19.490
And the ban was going on, is that correct?

00:02:19.490 --> 00:02:20.490
Yes.

00:02:20.490 --> 00:02:24.009
My mother was a baby when my grandparents got baptized.

00:02:24.009 --> 00:02:26.610
So she grew up in the truth.

00:02:26.610 --> 00:02:31.050
In fact, my grandmother was a pioneer under the ban for many years.

00:02:31.050 --> 00:02:35.169
Later, my two sisters and I were raising the truth.

00:02:35.169 --> 00:02:36.169
Very interesting.

00:02:36.169 --> 00:02:37.409
And Yo Notes, what about you?

00:02:37.409 --> 00:02:42.689
My parents were contacted by the witnesses 10 years before the ban was lifted.

00:02:42.689 --> 00:02:46.090
So my sister and I were also raised in the truth.

00:02:46.090 --> 00:02:47.729
So this is very interesting.

00:02:47.729 --> 00:02:52.889
Often we have talked about brothers who were faithful under ban, who were adults.

00:02:52.889 --> 00:02:55.250
But you were children while the ban was going on.

00:02:55.250 --> 00:02:56.490
And you stayed faithful.

00:02:56.490 --> 00:03:01.409
So, daily, do you remember what it was like going to meetings under ban?

00:03:01.409 --> 00:03:02.409
Yes.

00:03:02.409 --> 00:03:05.169
We met secretly in small groups.

00:03:05.169 --> 00:03:07.530
The friends would arrive at different times.

00:03:07.530 --> 00:03:12.330
But once everyone was inside the home, we would love the gate and the door and pull

00:03:12.330 --> 00:03:14.409
down all of the shades.

00:03:14.409 --> 00:03:17.610
The meetings were moved to a different location each week.

00:03:17.610 --> 00:03:18.610
Very interesting.

00:03:18.610 --> 00:03:23.330
Now, it must have been though that you probably had to miss a lot of meetings under ban.

00:03:23.330 --> 00:03:24.330
No.

00:03:24.330 --> 00:03:25.330
No.

00:03:25.330 --> 00:03:27.169
We didn't want to miss any opportunity to meet together.

00:03:27.169 --> 00:03:32.370
But were you frightened in these meetings where you pulled down on the shades that you

00:03:32.370 --> 00:03:35.090
might be discovered or arrested?

00:03:35.090 --> 00:03:37.889
You might think so, but the opposite was true.

00:03:37.889 --> 00:03:40.969
I felt the most safe when we were all together.

00:03:40.969 --> 00:03:42.969
You could feel Jehovah's protection.

00:03:43.009 --> 00:03:44.849
That's very touching.

00:03:44.849 --> 00:03:49.090
So, you know, did you and Deelia know each other growing up?

00:03:49.090 --> 00:03:50.090
Yes.

00:03:50.090 --> 00:03:55.449
We grew up in the same town, Negreste wash, so our families knew each other.

00:03:55.449 --> 00:03:59.530
So, did your families then occasionally attend the same meetings?

00:03:59.530 --> 00:04:00.530
No.

00:04:00.530 --> 00:04:02.009
We didn't.

00:04:02.009 --> 00:04:06.969
You see, my family was in a separate group from Deelia's family.

00:04:06.969 --> 00:04:08.289
In a separate group.

00:04:08.289 --> 00:04:10.650
Now, explain what you mean.

00:04:10.650 --> 00:04:16.569
You might remember Brother Losh's video from the 2018 annual meeting.

00:04:16.569 --> 00:04:22.610
He explained how government spies infiltrated the witnesses in Romania, and this made it

00:04:22.610 --> 00:04:26.009
difficult to know who to trust.

00:04:26.009 --> 00:04:30.850
This caused the witnesses to separate into two large groups.

00:04:30.850 --> 00:04:37.930
One group stayed in contact with warhead quarters in Brooklyn, and the other did not.

00:04:37.930 --> 00:04:41.290
But what groups continued to worship Jehovah?

00:04:41.290 --> 00:04:42.290
Amazing.

00:04:42.290 --> 00:04:47.290
So, you grew up both of you as Jehovah's Witnesses, but associating with different groups.

00:04:47.290 --> 00:04:51.930
Now, did one group view the other group as apostates?

00:04:51.930 --> 00:04:53.889
Generally, no.

00:04:53.889 --> 00:04:57.129
We didn't see the other group as apostates.

00:04:57.129 --> 00:04:59.730
Our beliefs were essentially the same.

00:04:59.730 --> 00:05:00.730
Yes.

00:05:00.730 --> 00:05:06.730
I should mention that when I was small, I remember my mother stayed up one night studying.

00:05:06.730 --> 00:05:11.290
But a whole night of study, meditation, and prayer, she decided to switch to the group

00:05:11.290 --> 00:05:13.009
connected to the main organization.

00:05:13.009 --> 00:05:18.009
So, that's why I grew up as a part of the group associated with the main organization.

00:05:18.009 --> 00:05:24.329
My, it sounds like your mother was very conscientious and set a really good example for you.

00:05:24.329 --> 00:05:30.209
I, I deeply appreciate her and my grandparents for being faithful examples and good teachers.

00:05:30.209 --> 00:05:31.209
Okay.

00:05:31.209 --> 00:05:34.250
When you say good teachers, what do you mean?

00:05:34.250 --> 00:05:38.610
For example, we have, we kept beehives in our garden.

00:05:38.610 --> 00:05:41.810
My mother helped us see how Jehovah made them to be industrious.

00:05:41.810 --> 00:05:45.850
Then, she drew the lesson that we can be industrious like the bees.

00:05:45.850 --> 00:05:49.329
In spite of the bend, we can stay busy serving Jehovah.

00:05:49.329 --> 00:05:53.129
Those must be some cherished memories, those lessons like that.

00:05:53.129 --> 00:05:59.930
Now, I wonder, at meetings, since the literature was banned, what did you study?

00:05:59.930 --> 00:06:04.410
Usually, there was one copy of the watchtower for the whole group.

00:06:04.410 --> 00:06:09.529
When the paragraph was read, we would listen and answer the question from memory.

00:06:09.529 --> 00:06:13.410
My goodness, you had to pay really close attention at the meetings.

00:06:13.410 --> 00:06:18.329
Were there ever times when you could get together in larger groups?

00:06:18.329 --> 00:06:26.250
We couldn't have assemblies and conventions, but we could have funerals, weddings,

00:06:27.250 --> 00:06:30.050
this became our assemblies and conventions.

00:06:30.050 --> 00:06:37.209
Sometimes, a funeral could have as many as 1,000 people, and it could last up to four hours.

00:06:37.209 --> 00:06:38.209
Wow.

00:06:38.209 --> 00:06:39.970
Now, what about songs?

00:06:39.970 --> 00:06:43.050
The songbook would have been part of the band literature.

00:06:43.050 --> 00:06:45.050
Could you sing songs at your meetings?

00:06:45.050 --> 00:06:49.730
I remember being a child, getting together to memorize the songs.

00:06:49.730 --> 00:06:50.769
We enjoyed it.

00:06:50.769 --> 00:06:52.610
It was entertainment for us.

00:06:52.610 --> 00:06:54.490
So, you memorized the songs?

00:06:54.490 --> 00:06:59.209
So, if someone called out a song number, you could sing the song for memory.

00:06:59.209 --> 00:07:00.209
Yes.

00:07:00.209 --> 00:07:01.209
Yes.

00:07:01.209 --> 00:07:03.730
What was going to school like under band?

00:07:03.730 --> 00:07:09.529
Our classmates, our neighbors, all knew we were Jehovah's Witnesses.

00:07:09.529 --> 00:07:16.970
Because when under band, we didn't hide our identity as a witness.

00:07:16.970 --> 00:07:24.930
We just hid things that government outlets, such as meetings, preaching, literature.

00:07:24.930 --> 00:07:29.889
So you must have been very determined to stay faithful in school.

00:07:29.889 --> 00:07:33.370
So whatever happened to the two groups?

00:07:33.370 --> 00:07:42.649
I'm happy to say they reunited as one organization in 1988, then the band was lifted in 1990.

00:07:42.649 --> 00:07:44.649
The brothers were overjoyed.

00:07:44.649 --> 00:07:49.129
I can imagine they must have felt a great deal of relief when they could go about their

00:07:49.129 --> 00:07:51.370
spiritual routine without the band.

00:07:51.370 --> 00:07:52.370
True.

00:07:52.370 --> 00:07:56.089
But I learned a lesson I never wanted to forget.

00:07:56.089 --> 00:08:00.850
Band or no band, we are always under attack by Satan.

00:08:00.850 --> 00:08:08.410
I saw brothers that stayed faithful during the band, but fell away once the band was lifted.

00:08:08.410 --> 00:08:15.769
As circumstance change, Satan will always look for new ways to attack us.

00:08:15.769 --> 00:08:22.290
So band or no band, we must stay close to Jehovah.

00:08:22.290 --> 00:08:25.689
Those are profound thoughts, you know.

00:08:25.689 --> 00:08:29.449
Well how is Jehovah blessing the work in Romania today?

00:08:29.449 --> 00:08:33.289
Today there are more than 40,000 witnesses in Romania.

